data.description: This 5 bedroom, 3 bath, 2 car garage home offers 2,110 sq ft in District 3. This home features hardwood floors, three bedrooms and two bathrooms upstairs along with a great size living room. The kitchen has a separate dining area that flows into the living room. The downstairs offers a great size family room, two bedrooms and a 3/4 bathroom. The home has an attached oversized 2 car garage and a long concrete driveway for RV parking on the left and side. The backyard is level and perfect for your family needs. This home does need TLC.
